Ferrovial, Abertis Interested in Spain Airports, Times Says

-- B y   L a n a n h   N g u y e n
-- 
2011-06-12T11:07:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-12/ferrovial-abertis-interested-in-spain-airports-times-says.html
Ferrovial SA (FER)  and  Abertis
Infraestructuras SA (ABE)  have expressed interest in buying Spain’s
Madrid and Barcelona airports, the Sunday Times reported, citing
infrastructure investors.  The government is selling the assets in an attempt to raise
money to help shore up the country’s finances. Spain has
appointed investment banks to oversee the transactions, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lananh Nguyen in London at 
 Lnguyen35@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dick Schumacher at 
 dschumacher@bloomberg.net . 